      "path": "index.html",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>{{userName}}</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: #09090b;\n      --surface: #131316;\n      --text: #ededf0;\n      --muted: #8b8b96;\n      --accent: #5eead4;\n      --accent-2: #a78bfa;\n      --border: #232329;\n    }\n\n    * {\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n\n    html {\n      scroll-behavior: smooth;\n    }\n\n    ::selection {\n      background: rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.25);\n    }\n\n    body {\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n      max-width: 720px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 0 24px;\n    }\n\n    /* Header / hero */\n    header {\n      position: relative;\n      padding: 96px 0 64px;\n    }\n\n    header::before {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: absolute;\n      top: -160px;\n      left: -120px;\n      width: 480px;\n      height: 480px;\n      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.08), transparent 70%);\n      pointer-events: none;\n    }\n\n    .avatar {\n      width: 88px;\n      height: 88px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-size: 32px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      color: var(--bg);\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.25);\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n      font-size: 40px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .tagline {\n      font-size: 20px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .intro {\n      font-size: 17px;\n      color: var(--text);\n      max-width: 60ch;\n    }\n\n    /* Sections */\n    section {\n      padding: 40px 0;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n\n    h2 {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n    }\n\n    /* Work / projects */\n    .card {\n      display: block;\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      padding: 20px 24px;\n      margin-bottom: 16px;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      color: inherit;\n      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;\n    }\n\n    .card:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      transform: translateY(-2px);\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.1);\n    }\n\n    .card h3 {\n      font-size: 17px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n\n    .card p {\n      font-size: 15px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n\n    /* Contact links */\n    .links {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .links a {\n      display: inline-block;\n      padding: 10px 18px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      color: var(--text);\n      text-decoration: none;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;\n    }\n\n    .links a:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      color: var(--accent);\n    }\n\n    footer {\n      padding: 40px 0 64px;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 480px) {\n      header {\n        padding: 64px 0 48px;\n      }\n\n      h1 {\n        font-size: 32px;\n      }\n\n      .tagline {\n        font-size: 18px;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <header>\n      <div class=\"avatar\">AK</div>\n      <h1>{{userName}}</h1>\n      <p class=\"tagline\">Software engineer &amp; builder</p>\n      <p class=\"intro\">\n        Hi, I'm {{userName}}. I build software and enjoy turning ideas into simple,\n        well-crafted tools. This is my corner of the internet — a place for\n        what I'm working on and how to reach me.\n      </p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2>What I'm working on</h2>\n      <a class=\"card\" href=\"#\">\n        <h3>Project One</h3>\n        <p>A short description of what this project does and why it exists.</p>\n      </a>\n      <a class=\"card\" href=\"#\">\n        <h3>Project Two</h3>\n        <p>Another thing I've built or am currently exploring.</p>\n      </a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2>Get in touch</h2>\n      <div class=\"links\">\n        <a href=\"mailto:<email>\">Email</a>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LinkedIn</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n      &copy; 2026 {{userName}}\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
    },
    {
      "path": "README.md",
      "content": "# My Page\n\nStarter workspace.\n"
    }
  ]
